    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到布拉沃汽车旅馆，一次清洁工作将揭开双重视角的恐怖故事。游戏始于艾莉森，一位逃离过去的女子，却在这里陷入了旅馆的邪恶陷阱。随后你将扮演艾玛，本以为找到了安全庇护所，却发现了令人毛骨悚然的真相。通过两个角色的双重视角，布拉沃汽车旅馆的恐怖真相逐渐浮出水面，颠覆你所有的认知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特色：</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎭 双重视角叙事</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过两个紧密相连的角色体验剧情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >视角转换揭示惊人真相</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >见证两条时间线的碰撞，揭示背后的恐怖真相</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧹 沉浸式清洁模拟</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全可互动的物理环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >细致入微的清洁动画，让每个动作都令人上瘾</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一边打扫，一边发现线索</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👻 心理恐怖</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超写实画面，模糊现实与游戏的界限</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着秘密揭露，紧张感逐步升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环境讲述的故事让你对现实产生怀疑</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔍 烧脑悬疑</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拼凑挑战认知的剧情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >见证同一事件的两种恐怖诠释</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开布拉沃汽车旅馆背后的邪恶面纱</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187540/extras/cc71aa1645d40659de56e17a7cec8a24.poster.avif?t=1734090727\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187540/extras/cc71aa1645d40659de56e17a7cec8a24.webm?t=1734090727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187540/extras/cc71aa1645d40659de56e17a7cec8a24.mp4?t=1734090727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187540/extras/5c201